title: Mentally Challenged Trump supporter Tortured in Chicago (Rant)
description:
Minutes after I put away all of my fancy film equipment I stumbled onto a Jeff Holiday video about a racial/political attack on someone, for allegedly being a Donald Trump supporter. The accused in this case are in custody, and the victim has been identified as a mentally ill youth. The four attackers bound and beat the victim, repeatedly mocked them and broadcast it with FaceBook Live. 

My rant is related to the incident, the ideology that I believe inspired it, misinformation, the misattribution of blame, and why Social Justice types seem to attack themselves.

News Source: http://www.fox32chicago.com/news/crime/227116738-story

Here is a link to Jeff's video on the attack: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zzb9FjbgXbg

Full video (it may be difficult to watch): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D5Hjr93KB1A

Hugh Mungus Reference video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RzA4dCT4X0I
